    <td width="320" ><p class="body1">primary mode of living is internally focused, where they deal with things according to how you feel about them, or how they fit into their personal value system. Their secondary mode is external, where they take things in primarily via their intuition.</p>

<p class="body1">INFPs main focus is on making the world a better place, more so than any other intuitive Type. Their purpose is focused on finding out the meaning of life. Idealistic and perfectionistic in nature, they drive themselves and others in a quest to achieve the goals they have identified. They are gifted at and excel at intuitive reading abilities related to people. These are used to guide them in combination with a continued search for value in life. They will stop at nothing to accumulate and to investigate knowledge which leads to help themselves and others to make the world a better place.
</p>
